data.content:
noun
plural ~ lists
[count] a list of names and addresses to which mail is sent
The charity sent out letters to everyone on its mailing list.
He asked the company to put him on their mailing list so that he could receive their catalog.
a list of names and e-mail addresses to which e-mails are sent by people who are on the list
People subscribe to Internet mailing lists in order to exchange information about special subjects.

danh sách những địa chỉ nhận thông tin bằng thư
I will put you on our mailing list, sir
thưa ông tôi sẽ ghi tên ông vào danh sách những địa chỉ nhận thông tin bằng thư của chúng tôi
